# Affiliate Compliance

## Required on every affiliate page

- Short FTC disclosure above the fold via `DisclosureBanner`
- Full disclosure in footer (from `affiliate/disclosure.md`)
- All Amazon links: `rel="nofollow sponsored"` and `target="_blank"`
- All Amazon links include `tag={associate_tag}` from `affiliate/config.yaml`
- Descriptive link text — never "click here" as sole text

## Prohibited

- Price guarantees or "lowest price" claims
- Incentivized click language ("click to support me")
- Amazon logo misuse or implied Amazon endorsement
- Copied Amazon product descriptions
- Publishing with `published: true` before `validate_affiliate_page.py` passes

## Before publish

Run `python scripts/validate_affiliate_page.py` and fix all errors.
